      "description": "Check out this dependable ride! It's a solid daily driver that has served its previous owners well and still has plenty of life left in it. While you'll notice some honest wear and tear on the body and interior, it's a fantastic, budget-friendly option for someone looking for reliable transportation without the showroom price tag.",
