      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior remains unblemished, while the cabin retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure performance that mirrors its initial delivery. This is an investment-grade example, offering an uncompromising driving experience for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
